Description:
    Generator of files for api resource

Example:
    rails g api_resource purchase

    This will create:
        - controller without searchkick
        - serializer
        - policy
        - specs without searchkick
        - factory
        - route

    rails g api_resource purchase --actions controller,specs --searchkick true

    This will create:
        - controller with searchkick
        - specs with searchkick
    
